		<td><b>Re: SFROM compatibility</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you duplicate the CHR ROM data to full the chip, you can use the SLROM board.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
