	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So Something like this dos command?<br />C:\Roms&gt;copy /b NESrom.chr + NESrom.chr + NESrom.chr + NESrom.chr NESromFinal.chr<br /><br />That I guess was my idea of padding it. <br /><br />I appreciate the response! <br /><br />Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

